OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FBarnsley Casualty is facing one of
OL,7,     Fits toughest shifts to date. With
OL,8,     Fno children's beds available
OL,9,     Facross the whole of Yorkshire, and
OL,10,     Fa department filling up with
OL,11,     Fchildren.
OL,12,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Natalia Spierings struggles to
OL,14,     Fsee acne hidden with makeup by a
OL,15,     Fpatient. Dr Toby Nelson is shocked
OL,16,     Fby a patient's DIY attempt on a
OL,17,     Fcyst. Dr Adil Sheraz tackles a
OL,18,     Fstubborn lipoma.
OL,19,G0335 Home and Away
OL,20,     FLacey lashes out. Richie feels the
OL,21,     Fweight of his actions. Cash takes
OL,22,     Fthe high road.
